392
00:30:43,319 --> 00:30:49,519
CONGRATULATIONS. I WISH YOU HAPPINESS.
BEAR ME A NEPHEW SOON. FROM SAEN.

393
00:31:07,319 --> 00:31:08,519
What are you doing?

