Nothing.

395
00:31:12,039 --> 00:31:14,400
-Then why were you looking at it?
-Sib.

396
00:31:15,359 --> 00:31:16,359
Do you miss him?

397
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,880
Is it that bad to live with me?

398
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:23,440
-I haven't said a word.
