405
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:43,759
Both of us raised him together.

406
00:31:43,839 --> 00:31:46,359
Raising our son is your job, not mine.

407
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:48,880
My job is to work and earn money.

408
00:31:49,559 --> 00:31:51,480
You are the reason he's like this.

409
00:31:53,559 --> 00:31:55,039
